              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Observations of the fission rates with",
                "thermal neutrons were made with and without a Cd",
                "shield covering the chamber. This shield reduced the",
                "fission rate to one per cent of the unshielded value.",
                "In the case of thermal-neutron measurements, the",
                "ionization chamber was situated approximately 3",
                "inches from the target and a block of paraffin",
                "approximately l8 inches on a side surrounded both the",
                "chamber and the target."
